who sprinkled scented powder on my face.

681
00:40:56,943 --> 00:40:59,903
So you knew all along
that the person back then was me.

682
00:40:59,903 --> 00:41:00,702
Of course.

683
00:41:01,142 --> 00:41:03,622
I've always been observant
of the finest detail.

684
00:41:05,543 --> 00:41:06,943
Then why didn't you catch me
at that time?

685
00:41:07,262 --> 00:41:11,863
Could it be that you had fallen for me
at first sight?

686
00:41:13,503 --> 00:41:15,662
At that time,
I felt you were very special

687
00:41:16,102 --> 00:41:16,983
and not at all simple.

688
00:41:17,782 --> 00:41:19,222
So I thought to spare you for a while

689
00:41:19,503 --> 00:41:21,423
to see if you could come up
with any new tricks.

690
00:41:24,343 --> 00:41:26,662
What about you?
When did you become fond of me?

691
00:41:29,102 --> 00:41:30,302
That's a secret.

692
00:41:31,023 --> 00:41:32,662
If you want to know...

693
00:41:40,182 --> 00:41:44,702
Actually, I don't know either.

694
00:41:45,463 --> 00:41:47,142
But suddenly, one day,

695
00:41:47,903 --> 00:41:49,063
I found

696
00:41:50,543 --> 00:41:54,823
